                   <li><a href="http://www.doi.gov/ppp/Strategic Plan FY07-12/strat_plan_fy2007_2012.pdf">DOI Strategic Plan</a> </li> 
                   <li><a href="http://library.usgs.gov/">USGS Library </a></li> 
